Must have:

- Form asking user to enter a topic update.
	A submit button beside to record the topic info into the database.

- 10 most recent posts from your friends.

- All registered user names are displayed. A textbox is displayed where a username can be entered to forcefully add that person as a friend.

On Page:

1. Large title with name of logged-in user
2. Logout link that sends user back to welcome/login page.
3. Status update box.
4. 10 most recent messages from friends.
5. List of all current members
6. Friend Request Box.



BACK END

- 2 CSV files as database


